Where Classics Meet Comfort

Vans has reinvigorated the iconic Classic Slip-On silhouette by introducing ComfyCush technology: a softer, cushiony outsole that gives the Slip-On ComfyCush Checkerboard a first-class fit that feels like walking on a cloud. Newly constructed checkerboard canvas uppers house simplified one-piece interiors with added arch support and moisture-wicking lining throughout, resulting in a lightweight experience that ensures you’ll Keep It Comfy at all times.

  • Iconic Slip-On shoe updated with ComfyCush™

  • Simplified one-piece interior

  • Added arch support

  • Rubber outsole for durability and traction

  • 6 oz canvas upper that focuses on tongue stabilization

  • Moisture-wicking lining materials

  • Signature checkerboard print
